---

<article
    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 md:flex-row"
>
    <div
        class="[&>p]:mb-4 [&>p>strong]:text-yellow-500 dark:[&>p>strong]:text-yellow-100 [&>p>strong]:font-normal [&>p>strong]:font-mono text-pretty order-2 md:order-1"
    >
        <p>
            I am Brayan Zavala, a passionate and committed developer with a
            solid background in web and mobile development. My professional
            career has focused on creating innovative and efficient digital
            tools, <strong
                >always seeking the perfect balance between functionality and
                design.
            </strong>
        </p>

        <p>
            Throughout my career, I have worked on various projects that have
            allowed me to develop skills in multiple languages and technologies.
            I have experience with tools like TypeScript, JavaScript and
            frameworks like React for frontend development. In the backend, I am
            proficient in Node.js, Java, and C#,
            <strong>
                enabling me to create comprehensive and robust solutions.</strong
            >
        </p>

        <p>
            My projects are often distinguished by their focus on performance
            and optimization, ensuring a fast and smooth experience for end
            users. I believe in the importance of teamwork and collaboration,
            actively participating with development teams. <strong
                >I am currently seeking new opportunities <em class="italic"
                    >to apply my knowledge and continue learning,</em
                >
            </strong> contributing to the development of technological solutions
            that make a difference.
        </p>
    </div>

    <img
        width="200"
        height="200"
        src="/brayan-zavala.jpg"
        alt={personalImageAlt}
        class="order-1 object-cover w-64 h-full p-1 md:order-2 rotate-3 lg:p-2 lg:w-64 aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-black/20 dark:bg-yellow-500/5 ring-1 ring-black/70 dark:ring-white/20"
        style="object-position: 50% 50%"
    />
</article>
